message:
Manifold core changes
- Some performance related changes stemming from IJ performance optimizations for large projects having 100s inter-related modules with several root modules e.g., the IJ open source project
- Enhance @Precompile so that a file extension can be used as an alternative to naming a type manifold class

added: * A base class for a type manifold that is based on a resource file type, typically discernible by the file extension.
* @param module  The module passed into the {@code ITypeManifold) implementation constructor
deleted: * A base class for a type manifold that is based on a resource file of a specific extension.
* @param module  The module passed into the ISourceProvider implementation constructor
